{"tid":2155902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"據報Google將停止回應香港當局索取數據要求","createTime":"2020-08-14T05:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T06:07:36.000Z","uid":227801,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ea0f360b525c0838d6b0c59ef0d59537429ea56","tid":2155902,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:47:46.000Z","msg":"谷歌據報將停止回應香港當局索取數據要求<br />\n<br />\n互聯網搜尋器谷歌據報將停止回應香港當局索取數據的要求。《華盛頓郵報》引述知情人士說，北京實施新國安法後，谷歌將停止與香港當局合作。谷歌星期四通知香港警方，取得數據要透過美國的《司法互助條約》作出請求，有關過程繁瑣，需要通過美國司法部處理，可能需要數星期甚至數月時間，安排等同將香港當成中國內地來處理。根據國案法，企業協助或保護被指涉嫌違反國安法的人，或拒絕當局索取資料的要求，也可能面臨拘捕。谷歌是其中一間美國科技企業在香港有分公司和員工，令他們在香港做生意的風險大增。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-14 13:34:32<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543705-20200814.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543705-20200814.htm&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBRx3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=aa5c8627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543705-20200814.htm&h=9febd24a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543705-20200814.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d28d8f7abc07a002d7091d7fc6c61725ef64c005","tid":2155902,"uid":179292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"早就應該啦"},{"pid":"e6623c70eaaa5865f544539e86e96a1b942c4a06","tid":2155902,"uid":205469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:50:02.000Z","msg":"Google傻仔嚟<br />\n俾流料，半真半假咩得囉"},{"pid":"668875977a8787569bd1aec5952a819d7f197faf","tid":2155902,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:50:31.000Z","msg":"其實不嬲都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff03c3e0f598428d972a416638aa21ef6913f25","tid":2155902,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class